reviews.review_text: GRATE sounding shows by you!!!!!!!!! The shows you record are amazing, I swear they're best sounding AUD shows I've ever heard. Thank You so much.
Nice Absolutely Stellar recording of an average if not uninspired show.  And that's a damn shame.

Excellent. The first set is a fantastic recording of a very good performance. Yes, there are a few little weakspots here and there, but also some absolutely killer versions of some songs. Phil is great all over this set and the BASS is really strong for an audience tape. The sound is really fantastic overall.

Set 2 stumbles a bit in the China>Rider, BUT....this show has a really great Drums>Space...just THUNDERING drums and a really creative space. The Wheel thru Sat. Night are all excellent. Sound is sweet, like set 1.
